  • public class Registrations
extends java.lang.Object
    Global registration of baggage handlers to keys. Not currently implemented to support adding new handlers at runtime

      • register

        public static void register(BagKey key,
                            BaggageHandler<?> handler)
        Registers the provided key with the provided handler into the process's default registrations. HIGHLY recommended NOT to do this -- instead you should statically configure the registration of keys to handlers. However, for trialling code and testing, this is an easier way to avoid error messages.
